    <!-- Application Structure Plan: The SPA is structured as an interactive executive dashboard (Top-Down flow). 
         1. 'Executive Summary' introduces the market sizing (the 'what').
         2. 'Competitive Landscape' allows deep dives into specific brands via an interactive selector, updating text and charts dynamically to prevent information overload (the 'who').
         3. 'Channel & Consumer Preferences' groups related distribution/flavor data (the 'where and how').
         4. 'Regulatory & Client Alignment' covers the constraints and non-negotiable inputs required to finalize strategy. 
         This dashboard structure is chosen to make dense competitive intelligence easily explorable, allowing brand managers to filter data by competitor or focus area without leaving the page. -->
    
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
